Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.64,0:01:32.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走嘛  走嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.50,0:01:35.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.18,0:01:37.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之跟我們走就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.98,0:01:40.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說要去哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.49,0:01:42.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走嘛  走嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.74,0:01:44.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走嘛  走嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.66,0:01:45.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.76,0:01:55.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.23,0:01:57.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你很久了  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.83,0:02:00.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.98,0:02:03.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班長的命令拒絕不了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.91,0:02:05.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.31,0:02:07.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.38,0:02:10.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  進去吧  進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.31,0:02:25.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有時會發出很可疑的騷動  還會聽到奇怪的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.76,0:02:27.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有感覺到什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.19,0:02:29.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…  我也不會感覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.36,0:02:36.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管夏目你怎麼否認  我始終相信你有種特別的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.32,0:02:43.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許你並不喜歡  但我覺得那是很了不起的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.80,0:02:45.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該更自信一點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.90,0:02:49.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  說來西村和北本呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.01,0:02:52.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:53.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.88,0:02:56.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用去管那些不相信的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.19,0:03:01.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.01,0:03:05.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實像是會有妖怪的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.45,0:03:06.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.45,0:03:07.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多軌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.81,0:03:10.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很有意思  我也一起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.66,0:03:17.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  {\fe128\fscx80\fscy92\fnDFPTFLeiSho-W5}笹{\r}田同學  我們去對面看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.64,0:03:20.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目就去看那邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.89,0:03:22.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.89,0:03:24.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行啦  行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.46,0:03:25.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是想跟夏目…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:25.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.83,0:03:30.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個叫多軌的小姑娘  還挺機靈的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.10,0:03:31.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.31,0:03:34.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了  我們趕快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.65,0:03:37.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個地方確實不宜久留
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:40.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為什麼  真的有什麼在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.33,0:03:41.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.20,0:03:45.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  在對方沒發現我們之前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.11,0:03:47.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  喂  你去哪！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.16,0:03:51.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話多軌她們也有危險  我去叫她們回來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.25,0:03:54.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙實在是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.44,0:04:01.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.00,0:04:05.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的聲音  小孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.31,0:04:09.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  說不定那不是人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.65,0:04:10.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.41,0:04:41.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棺材？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.70,0:04:47.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  打開！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.44,0:04:49.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.45,0:04:50.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在裡面？等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.14,0:04:52.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在就打開
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.77,0:04:54.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.69,0:05:02.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.69,0:05:11.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.41,0:05:13.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完美的上勾拳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.15,0:05:16.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子怎麼會被關在這裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.12,0:05:20.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從氣味來看  似乎不是妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.31,0:05:22.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在玩捉迷藏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.38,0:05:28.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許是不小心蓋子掉下來  就出不來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.51,0:05:30.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.79,0:05:33.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像聽到有聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.10,0:05:37.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不  沒什麼  你們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.46,0:05:40.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾  什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.09,0:05:44.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  在這裡  貓咪！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.04,0:05:44.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驚！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.42,0:05:49.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.29,0:05:51.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧…興趣真差
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.61,0:05:54.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:05:57.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.70,0:06:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石尾海？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.12,0:06:05.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三班那個  就是被怪人追的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.43,0:06:06.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.27,0:06:09.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像還說可能是妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.13,0:06:13.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會是因為父母回家都很晚  他才變得說這種話了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.89,0:06:16.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他被人欺負嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.13,0:06:20.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會  不知怎麼的他朋友很多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.26,0:06:22.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.53,0:06:23.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掰掰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.64,0:06:24.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.75,0:06:35.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓咪老師！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.23,0:06:37.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.71,0:06:42.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你把我關進箱子裡的嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.86,0:06:45.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.21,0:06:49.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就說不是我了  我是來給你送東西的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.23,0:06:52.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.69,0:06:53.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這傢伙在追著你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.16,0:06:55.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾開！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.25,0:06:56.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.34,0:07:00.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看  他還帶著隻超醜的貓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.09,0:07:02.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好土！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:03.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醜？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.43,0:07:06.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是豬？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.12,0:07:06.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.66,0:07:10.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾遠點！豆芽！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.00,0:07:11.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜板！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.25,0:07:12.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樸樹！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.47,0:07:13.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人妖！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.53,0:07:14.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾開！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.88,0:07:15.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先逃吧  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.59,0:07:20.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  逃了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.57,0:07:21.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准再來！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.75,0:07:22.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.02,0:07:24.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒什麼大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.38,0:07:26.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是  輕輕鬆鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.56,0:07:29.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  海你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.66,0:07:33.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.62,0:07:38.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉唉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.87,0:07:41.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說不定不會應付小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.75,0:07:42.50,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（豆芽）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.60,0:07:43.25,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（菜板）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.35,0:07:44.00,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（樸樹）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.10,0:07:45.20,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（人妖）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.84,0:07:49.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比跟妖怪對峙受到的傷害還大…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.15,0:07:51.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真夠煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.25,0:07:54.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不好  這個忘記給他了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.88,0:07:56.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  名牌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.45,0:08:01.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  老師  你幫我帶給那孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.05,0:08:03.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你200日元
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.54,0:08:08.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！居然想用區區200日元就打發我這高貴的妖怪！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.59,0:08:11.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要紙的！紙鈔！給我福澤諭吉！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.59,0:08:11.45,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（福澤諭吉：萬元鈔）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.55,0:08:21.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被妖怪追著…那孩子也能看見妖怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.46,0:08:24.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  田沼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.12,0:08:32.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看見妖怪的孩子…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.02,0:08:35.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  也不像被人欺負
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.77,0:08:38.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.62,0:08:40.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.38,0:08:45.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了他  那個小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.97,0:08:57.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是破壞了約定  就吃了他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.51,0:08:59.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.64,0:09:09.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.19,0:09:11.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.12,0:09:17.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它說的小鬼是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.30,0:09:19.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.14,0:09:21.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  多軌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.00,0:09:23.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這裡做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.47,0:09:25.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  剛才…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.19,0:09:28.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  你是第一次見到田沼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.86,0:09:31.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是五班的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.02,0:09:34.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這話等一下再說  趕快離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.09,0:09:39.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家裡有書上寫了  說這附近會吸引妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.21,0:09:41.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸引妖怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.79,0:09:46.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  你流血了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.04,0:09:50.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候…  是剛才那傢伙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.64,0:09:55.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血的味道會引來妖怪  快走吧  你也是！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.73,0:10:04.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祖輩是陰陽師？所以才…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.75,0:10:07.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  這就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.22,0:10:08.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.88,0:10:11.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是很兇暴的妖怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.12,0:10:18.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不能對妖怪心軟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.78,0:10:23.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為它們與人不同  是邪惡的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.85,0:10:29.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個叫海的孩子  真的能看到妖怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.99,0:10:32.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚  不過如果能看到的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.46,0:10:34.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想保護他？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.73,0:10:37.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.34,0:10:39.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.77,0:10:45.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到不能坐視不管  就會馬上出手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.88,0:10:49.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事  或許是我太傲慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.31,0:10:51.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.98,0:10:58.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果  只覺得是自己在找麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.39,0:11:04.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久之前  還全都怪在妖怪頭上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.82,0:11:34.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.99,0:11:35.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妖怪嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.89,0:11:37.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.61,0:11:45.87,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（你掉的東西）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.08,0:11:45.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉…掉的東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.70,0:11:51.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得好  貓咪老師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.61,0:11:59.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊  會給你的  回去給你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.99,0:12:01.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忍不住了～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.48,0:12:04.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又  又是你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.98,0:12:06.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓咪  貓咪～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.48,0:12:07.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的興趣真差勁啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.53,0:12:09.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.03,0:12:12.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟在我後面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.48,0:12:21.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不是你嗎  不是你在追我  把我關進箱子裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.95,0:12:24.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.23,0:12:29.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…之前的  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.76,0:12:35.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…說你是豆芽  菜板  人妖什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.41,0:12:39.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  啊  不…沒關係…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.99,0:12:44.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼好笑的！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.62,0:12:46.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.00,0:12:48.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再見  我道過歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.22,0:12:49.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.44,0:12:56.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於那個追著你的傢伙  告訴警察比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.31,0:12:59.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  跟他們說了也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.02,0:13:01.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會沒用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.00,0:13:04.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我道過歉了  你就別管我了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.79,0:13:07.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  受傷了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.78,0:13:08.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.89,0:13:14.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別耍這種無聊的脾氣！等到事情嚴重了就太晚了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.66,0:13:18.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.55,0:13:23.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對不起  我這麼大聲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.68,0:13:27.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.86,0:13:33.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像沒斷  過幾天就不會痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.17,0:13:35.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.49,0:13:39.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.41,0:14:10.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把小孩子弄哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.27,0:14:14.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底該如何把我的擔心傳達給他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.83,0:14:19.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面對妖怪反而交往得更輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.64,0:14:28.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒想給你添麻煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.82,0:14:34.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是剛好看到了  你的手受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.25,0:14:40.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就想會不會是為了救我  被追著我的傢伙攻擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.53,0:14:45.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以這次就由我來保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.20,0:14:48.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才跟過來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.72,0:14:51.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.71,0:14:57.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再  再見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.19,0:15:05.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家裡人還沒回來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.37,0:15:07.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一個人嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.01,0:15:13.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人說要保護我  這還是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.79,0:15:19.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我等一下  你把我當成什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.70,0:15:21.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.79,0:15:23.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師是我的保鏢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:28.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准忘！也不好笑！真討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.26,0:15:41.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  小妖怪而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.06,0:15:46.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追著我來了的話  它的目標就不是海嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.64,0:15:48.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它盯上海了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.98,0:15:51.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  但是它說過要吃掉小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.35,0:15:54.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃小孩子的妖怪有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.54,0:15:58.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你想太多了  區區小妖怪的戲言而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.27,0:16:01.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說小妖怪  我剛才還被它弄傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.78,0:16:04.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？在我不知道的時候？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.36,0:16:06.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一點小傷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.94,0:16:11.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呆子！雖然你被吃掉我就能得到友人帳是很好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.91,0:16:15.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但讓那種小妖怪弄傷我的東西  我心情是很微妙的！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.67,0:16:17.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常微妙！你懂不懂夏目！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.97,0:16:20.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這微妙的心情！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.15,0:16:21.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.06,0:16:23.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微妙——
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.54,0:16:30.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那如果海看不到妖怪的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.49,0:16:33.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盯上海的不是妖怪的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.41,0:16:36.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是誰把海關進棺材裡的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.67,0:16:42.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  你在看什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.85,0:16:43.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.35,0:16:45.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  那孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.10,0:16:50.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真可愛  是在等人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.33,0:16:52.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.90,0:17:01.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想  保護那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.94,0:17:13.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那以來  我每天放學後都和海一起度過
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.14,0:17:19.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是多軌教我的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.11,0:17:20.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.69,0:17:24.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下就一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.54,0:17:38.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.90,0:17:40.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.48,0:17:43.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能告訴我了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.30,0:17:45.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個箱子？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.00,0:17:48.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你不願意就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.87,0:17:53.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早些時候  我就覺得被誰盯著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.38,0:17:56.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來發現電線杆後面有人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.10,0:18:00.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始以為只是變態  就沒太在意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.08,0:18:03.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  這應該在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.58,0:18:11.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天  我被那傢伙追趕  跑進了那棟房子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.23,0:18:14.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來是想躲進那個箱子裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.42,0:18:17.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果就出不來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.25,0:18:19.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箱子被鎖上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.31,0:18:20.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎖上了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.05,0:18:25.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候  我記得沒有鎖…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.32,0:18:30.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.68,0:18:37.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.36,0:18:43.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多軌看不見  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.99,0:18:45.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看得到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.62,0:18:49.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  這麼說  夏目也看得見那個？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.22,0:18:53.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多軌  這裡有妖怪！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.67,0:18:54.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.95,0:18:57.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帶著海往這邊逃  你別追過來！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.47,0:18:59.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.34,0:18:59.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.51,0:19:05.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.22,0:19:12.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.32,0:19:13.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.00,0:19:15.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.31,0:19:23.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…  糟糕  被引過來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.01,0:19:31.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海  快逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.41,0:19:34.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.09,0:19:42.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.91,0:19:46.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓咪老師！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.31,0:19:52.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我  放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.69,0:19:55.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.83,0:19:56.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我放它走的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.55,0:20:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃掉的話你會很煩  而且我是個美食家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.71,0:20:05.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它的妖氣吸走了不少  應該不會再來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.63,0:20:07.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼知道是這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.03,0:20:11.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多軌面無血色地跑來找我  過來一看就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.56,0:20:13.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要到什麼時候才會長記性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.35,0:20:19.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是多軌…是嗎  老師  謝謝你  得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.45,0:20:23.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別摸鼻子！很癢的！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.45,0:20:26.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害  好厲害啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.16,0:20:29.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目能馴服妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.61,0:20:32.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是馴服  是它救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.69,0:20:35.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目！海！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.92,0:20:37.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多軌！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.06,0:20:41.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  你們沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.30,0:20:44.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  多虧了老師
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.17,0:20:48.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓咪！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.42,0:20:51.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了夠了夠了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.54,0:20:51.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.01,0:20:54.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海能看見妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.09,0:20:58.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼追趕他的是剛才那個妖怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.89,0:21:01.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.50,0:21:04.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得好像還沒結束…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.78,0:21:11.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.22,0:21:15.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他把海關進棺材裡的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.99,0:21:28.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名  名取先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.19,0:21:33.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  這次特意不想把你捲進來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.91,0:21:36.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到你自己牽扯過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.02,0:21:39.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  把海關進棺材裡的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.28,0:21:43.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是關進去  而是封印
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.20,0:21:43.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.23,0:21:48.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是不要接近那孩子比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.99,0:21:52.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  到底是怎麼回事  名取先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.07,0:21:56.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  那孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.60,0:22:01.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.02,0:23:50.02,biaoti1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(150,550)}人與妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.04,0:23:37.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海竟然是妖怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.55,0:23:39.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了消滅他才來的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.97,0:23:43.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他做了什麼！海做了什麼要被人消滅的事嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.27,0:23:45.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  你也該下定決心了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.88,0:23:49.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你來說重要的  到底是人  還是妖怪


